  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tam ne buhs Lehgeri nahkt/ un kad wiꞥſch prett Wak- karu ar Uhdeni pehrtees/ tad buhs winnam/ kad ta Saute irr no- gahjuft eekſch Lehgera nahkt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Laid tew arridsan kahda Weeta ahra preekſch Lehgera irr/ un us turren buhs tew iseet ah- ra tawas Watjadsibas dehk.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tad laid tew kahda Lahpstite pee (zittahm) tawahim Leetahm irr/ un kad tu ahra feh- defi/ tad buhs tew ar to ahra rakt/ un atgreestees/ un apraust/ kas no tewim iggahjis irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tas KUNGS taws Deews staiga tawâ Lehgeri tew atpestidams/ un tawus Eenaids- neekus tawâ Preekscha nodoh- dams/ tapehz buhs tarwam Leh- geram fwehtam buht/ ka wiꞥſch ne kahdn Kauna Leetu tawâ Starpâ eeredſ/ un no tewim at- pakkat atgreeschahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tew ne buhs to Kalpu winna Kungam nodoht/ kas no tawa Kunga pee tewim igglah- bees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Laid tas pee tew paleek tawâ Widdû / tai Weetâ/ ko wiꞥſch istredsehs/ jeb kahdâs no tawahm Wahrtim / winnam par labbu/ tew ne buhs winnam pahri darriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Laid ne kahda Mauka irr starp Israëta Meitahm/ neds Manzineeks starp Israëta Deh- leem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tew ne buhs ne kahdn megs- Algu neds Sunnu-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Naudu eekſch ta KUNGA ta wa Deewa Namma nest/ par jeb- kuru Apfohlifchanu/ jo tee abb irr tam KUNGAM tawam Dee- wam weena Negantiba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tew ne buhs no taw Brahta Augtus dſiht/neds Nau das Augtus / neds Barribas Augtus/ neds jebkurras Leetas Augtus/ar ko warr Augtus dſiht\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No Swescheim tew buhe Angkus dſiht/ bet no tawa Brahta tew ne buhs Augtus dſiht ka tas KUNGS taws Deew tew fwehti eekſch wiſta/ pee ka tu tawu Rohku issteepi / tai Sem mê/ us kurren tu eij winnam ee mantoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad tu tam KUNGAM tawam Deewain effi apfohlijees tad tew ne buhs faweht winnamakſaht/ jo tas KUNGS taw Deews to teefchain no tewim praffihs / zittadi tas tew pa Grehku nahktohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad tu wairs ne fohti tad tas tew par Grehku ne nah- fees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas no tawahm Luhpahm iseet/ to buhs tew turreht un dar riht / ittin ka tu tam KUNgam tawam Deewam weenn Uppur no labba Prahta fohlijs effi / ka tu ar tawu Mutti runnajs effi\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad tu tawa Tuwaka Wihtnu-Dahrsâ eti/ tad warri tu Ohgas ehst/ ka tew tiht/ kamehr tu pee-ehdi/bet eekſch tawa Trau ka tew ne buhs ne ko eelikt.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
